snippet.title: Save The World Tribe
snippet.description:
Hey there beautiful soul, welcome to Save The World Tribe! 

We are a community based organization that is dedicated to #OperationSaveTheWorld and developing the #SaveTheWorldTribe. Our main aim is to assist global spiritual revolution, resulting in a healthy society that supports your dreams.

Here you will find videos that enhance the collective consciousness, dive into the depths of life, and discuss awakening events.

Founded by Vesuvius Percival, a passionate spirit guide and revolutionary who is working on blueprints for rebuilding the world, Save The World Tribe is the community whose goal is to show you how to listen to your spiritual heart, reclaim your sovereignty, and wield your power of perception that is the awakening of consciousness. In this way, as a result, the entire world collective will become a better place for all, thus we will be able to save the world.

We hope to see you around, friend.
